.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Richardsons-Photo-by-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_BAFTA_Getty-Images-for-BAFTA.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Richardsons-Photo-by-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_BAFTA_Getty-Images-for-BAFTA-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Richardsons-Photo-by-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_BAFTA_Getty-Images-for-BAFTA-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Richardsons-Photo-by-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_BAFTA_Getty-Images-for-BAFTA-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Richardsons-Photo-by-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_BAFTA_Getty-Images-for-BAFTA-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Richardsons-Photo-by-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_BAFTA_Getty-Images-for-BAFTA-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>喜剧演员乔恩·理查森 (Jon Richardson) 和露西·博蒙特 (Lucy Beaumont) 在今天（4 月 12 日）的一份声明中透露，他们在结婚九年后分居了。</p><p>在声明中，这对夫妇表示，他们“共同友好地做出了离婚并分道扬镳的艰难决定”。</p><p>他们继续说道：“由于我们唯一的首要任务是为我们的女儿处理这一困难的过渡，因此我们要求在这个敏感时刻尊重我们的隐私，以保护她的福祉。</p><p> “我们不会发表进一步评论。”</p><p>自 2020 年起，这对夫妇就一起主演了<i>《拜见理查森一家》。</i>在这部纪录片中，他们扮演“夸张版的自己”。</p><p>两人还一起出演了<i>《Celebrity Gogglebox》</i>的多次演出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5qgV1li6eR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 