雷西·怀尔斯 (Tracey Wiles) 因在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-3">《博德之门 3》</a></em>中扮演卡拉赫和贾希拉的演员而获得奖项，在进场前摆了张合影。</p><h3><strong>说到风格……</strong> </h3><figure id="attachment_3617052" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617052" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617052" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games.jpg" alt="Chandana Ekanayake（左）和 Meghna Jayanth（右）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617052" class="wp-caption-text"> Chandana Ekanayake（左）和 Meghna Jayanth（右）。图片来源：Shane Anthony Sinclair/BAFTA/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Chandana Ekanayake 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2022-meghna-jayanth-is-switching-the-narrative-3331160">Meghna Jayanth</a>在代表<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/outerloop-games">Outerloop Games</a>的非凡角色扮演游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/thirsty-suitors"><em>《Thirsty Suitors》</em></a>时盛装打扮。</p><h3><strong>红地毯上的蜘蛛侠</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617055" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617055" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617055" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-Yuri-Lowenthal-Spider-Man-2.jpg" alt="纳吉·杰特和尤里·洛文塔尔。图片来源：BAFTA 的 Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-Yuri-Lowenthal-Spider-Man-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-Yuri-Lowenthal-Spider-Man-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-Yuri-Lowenthal-Spider-Man-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-Yuri-Lowenthal-Spider-Man-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-Yuri-Lowenthal-Spider-Man-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-Yuri-Lowenthal-Spider-Man-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617055" class="wp-caption-text">纳吉·杰特和尤里·洛文塔尔。图片来源：Shane Anthony Sinclair / BAFTA 盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>在这里插入指向蜘蛛侠模因的蜘蛛侠，纳吉·杰特（迈尔斯·莫拉莱斯饰）和尤里·洛文塔尔（彼得·帕克饰）来到这里庆祝他们在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/marvels-spider-man-2">漫威蜘蛛侠 2</a></em>中的出色表演。</p><h3> <strong>《<em>博德之门 3》</em>和<em>《心灵杀手</em><em>2》</em>联动，我们不知道我们需要什么</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617051" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617051" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617051" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-David-Harewood-and-Neil-Newbon.jpg" alt="大卫·哈伍德（左）和尼尔·纽邦（右）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-David-Harewood-and-Neil-Newbon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-David-Harewood-and-Neil-Newbon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-David-Harewood-and-Neil-Newbon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/u