rong><em>《古墓丽影》</em>明星雪莱金发女郎亮相</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617057" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617057" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617057" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games.jpg" alt="雪莉·金发，劳拉·克劳馥的配音。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617057" class="wp-caption-text">雪莉·金发，劳拉·克劳馥的配音。图片来源：凯特·格林/英国电影和电视艺术学院/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>雪莉·金发 (Shelley Blonde <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gamers-vote-lara-croft-as-the-most-iconic-character-in-gaming-3612798">) 饰演的角色劳拉·克劳馥 (Lara Croft) 被评为游戏界最具标志性的角色</a>几天后，人们发现她在英国电影和电视艺术学院游戏 (BAFTA Games) 的后台庆祝。</p><h3><strong>蜘蛛侠归来</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617054" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617054" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617054" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood.jpg" alt="纳吉·杰特和大卫·哈伍德。图片来源：BAFTA，盖蒂图片社" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617054" class="wp-caption-text">纳吉·杰特和大卫·哈伍德。图片来源：Scott Garfitt / BAFTA via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>纳吉·杰特 (Nadji Jeter) 回归，但这次他带着奖项，大卫·哈伍德 (David Harewood) 因其在迈尔斯·莫拉莱斯 (Miles Morales) 中的表演而授予他“最佳表演者”奖。</p><h3> <strong>“取景器”团队度过了一个盛大的夜晚</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617058" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617058" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617058" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games.jpg" alt="乔治·巴克、格温德林·福斯特和马修·斯塔克庆祝“取景器”。图片来源：BAFTA 的 Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617058" class="wp-caption-text">乔治·巴克、格温德林·福斯特和马修·斯塔克庆祝“取景器”。图片来源：Shane Anthony Sinclair / BAFTA / Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>很少有团队能像 Sad Owl Studios 那样值得庆祝，这家苏格兰开发商是华丽的独立热门游戏《Viewfinder》的开发商——请务必观看他们<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cy8yJqxpbo0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">激动人心的最佳英国游戏获奖感言</a>。</p><h3><strong>后台与今晚的表演者一起</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617053" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617053" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617053" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA.jpg" alt="朱莉·埃尔文、丹尼尔·奥茨和亚伦·格莱姆斯。图片来源：BAFTA 的 Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617053" class="wp-caption-text">朱莉·埃尔文、丹尼尔·奥茨和亚伦·格莱姆斯。图片来源：凯特·格林/英国电影和电视艺术学院/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>Julie Elven（左）、Daniel Oates（中）和 Aaron Grimes（右）翻唱了 Poets Of The Fall 的歌曲《Late Goodbye》，向游戏行业失去的人们致敬。</p><h3> <strong>《博德之门 3》统治了夜晚</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617050" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617050" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617050" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3.jpg" alt="Larian Studios 在 BAFTA Games 评选最佳游戏" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617050" class="wp-caption-text"> BAFTA Games 的 Larian Studios 为《博德之门 3》收集最佳游戏。图片来源：Stuart Wilson/BAFTA/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>总体而言，Larian Studios 赢得了最多奖项，包括最佳游戏。他们在这里，试图分享这个舞台。</p><p> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-wins-big-at-2024-bafta-games-awards-3616957">请在此处查看完整的获奖者名单</a>。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bafta-games-2024-in-pictures-big-wins-coffee-breaks-and-fashion-flexes-3617037">2024 年 BAFTA 运动会后的图片：重大胜利、茶歇和时尚展示</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
盖·里奇说亨利·卡维尔在女人进入房间时“总是”站起来https://www.nme.com/news/film/guy-ritchie-says-henry-cavill-always-stands-up-when-a-woman-enters-the-room-3617066?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=盖·里奇说，当女人进入房间时，亨利·卡维尔总是站起来Elizabeth AubreyFri, 12 Apr 2024 15:06:00 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3617066 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亨利·卡维尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两人最近合作拍摄了《不绅士战争部》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/guy-ritchie-says-henry-cavill-always-stands-up-when-a-woman-enters-the-room-3617066">盖·里奇 (Guy Ritchie) 称亨利·卡维尔 (Henry Cavill) 在女性进入房间时“总是”站起来的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亨利·卡维尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Henry-Cavill-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guy-ritchie">盖·里奇</a>表示，当一名女性进入房间时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/henry-cavill">亨利·卡维尔</a>“总是”站起来。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/guy-ritchie-ministry-of-ungentlemanly-warfare-movie-plot-alan-ritchson-1235868406/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》采访</em></a>时，里奇谈到了他们的新片<em>《不绅士战争部》，</em>他解释了为什么电影中的这群男人“不绅士”，然后分享说卡维尔恰恰相反，只要有女人进入房间，他就会站起来。</p><p>里奇说：“每当有女士走进房间时，亨利·卡维尔就会站起来。他自始至终都坚持这一点。我和他一起拍了两部电影。当一位女士走进来时，你从来不会不站起来。”</p><p>卡维尔回答：“给你！”然后改变话题讨论他的一位演员。</p><p>您可以在这里观看采访片段： </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@hollywoodreporter/video/7355966442761735466" data-video-id="7355966442761735466" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@好莱坞记者" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@hollywoodreporter?refer=embed">@好莱坞记者</a></p><p>“当一位女士走进房间时，你永远不会不站起来。”—— <a title="不绅士的战争" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/ungentlemanlywarfare?refer=embed">#ungentlemanlywarfare</a>导演<a title="盖里奇" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/guyritchie?refer=embed">#guyritchie</a>分享<a title="亨利·卡维尔" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/henrycavill?refer=embed">#henrycavill</a>所做的最绅士的事情是什么</p><p><a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - 好莱坞报道 - 好莱坞报道" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-The-Hollywood-Reporter-7355966644155337514?refer=embed">♬ 原声 – 好莱坞报道 – 好莱坞报道</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p> 这部动作喜剧由盖·里奇执导，灵感源自二战期间英国首相温斯顿·丘吉尔成立的第一个特种部队组织的真实故事，该组织帮助改变了战争的进程。</p><p>剧情简介如下：“这支绝密作战部队由一群流氓和特立独行者组成，他们使用完全非传统且完全‘不绅士’的战斗技术，执行一项大胆的对抗纳粹的任务。</p><p> “最终，他们大胆的做法改变了战争进程，并为英国特种空勤团和现代黑色行动战争奠定了基础。”</p><p>卡维尔领衔主演格斯·马奇-菲利普斯，与埃扎·冈萨雷斯、艾伦·里奇森、亚历克斯·帕蒂弗、赫罗·费因斯·蒂芬、巴布斯·奥卢萨莫昆、恩里克·扎加、蒂尔·施威格、亨利·戈尔丁和加利·艾尔维斯搭档。</p><p>除了担任导演之外，里奇还与保罗·塔马西、埃里克·约翰逊和阿拉什·阿梅尔共同撰写了剧本。他还与杰里·布鲁克海默、查德·奥曼、伊万·阿特金森和约翰·弗里德伯格一起担任制片人。</p><p>这是继 2015 年的<em>《来自 UNCLE 的男人》之</em>后卡维尔与里奇的第二次合作。他还将与导演在第三部目前尚未命名的动作片中重聚。</p><p>这也是里奇在过去十二个月内的第三部电影，继<em>《财富行动：战争的诡计》</em>和杰克·吉伦哈尔主演的<em>《契约》</em>之后。今年 3 月，这位导演还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-the-trailer-for-guy-ritchies-new-series-the-gentleman-starring-ray-winstone-vinnie-jones-3571160">Netflix 上首次推出了<em>《绅士》</em>的电视剧衍生剧</a>。</p><p> <strong><em>《非君子战争部》</em>将于 2024 年 4 月 19 日在电影院上映。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/guy-ritchie-says-henry-cavill-always-stands-up-when-a-woman-enters-the-room-3617066">盖·里奇 (Guy Ritchie) 称亨利·卡维尔 (Henry Cavill) 在女性进入房间时“总是”站起来的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
